item.title: Website Developer; Team_Developer
item.dc:creator: @Ruby_Forums_Coder Ruby
item.description:
@Ruby_Forums_Coder wrote:

What the fuck is this.

If people want a website made they can feel free to PM anyone, there’s no need for a topic like this. Also, what makes you qualified to make a website and declare yourself the lead developer of a team such as this? Especially when you create topics such as this. I’m fine with people creating websites for each other and stuff like that but I don’t see what the point in this is, people post in this board to have help given to them, there’s no point in just giving them a website, give them the materials to learn how to make one themselves.

Read full topic
